    "abstract": "kRPC allows you to control the game from external programs. It comes with client libraries for several popular languages including Python, C++, C#, Java and Lua. Programs communicate with the game over a TCP/IP connection, and can be configured to work on just the local machine or even over the wider internet. [All download links for this mod have been accelerated by KERBCAT.COM]",
